org.openimaj.feature.local.data

Class LocalFeatureListDataSource<T extends LocalFeature<?,? extends ArrayFeatureVector<F>>,F>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.data.AbstractDataSource<DATATYPE>
      • org.openimaj.data.AbstractMultiListDataSource<F,T>
        • org.openimaj.feature.local.data.LocalFeatureListDataSource<T,F>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of LocalFeature
    F - The type of FeatureVector.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<F>, DataSource<F>

    public class LocalFeatureListDataSource<T extends LocalFeature<?,? extends ArrayFeatureVector<F>>,F>
extends AbstractMultiListDataSource<F,T>
    A DataSource for the feature vector of one or more lists of LocalFeatures that use an ArrayFeatureVector for the feature vector. This can be used as a convenience when you want to feed multiple lists of local features to a clustering algorithm.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
